<ul><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#ebay">What is the difference between buying from Bridal Online versus buying from a store or on eBay?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#Secure">Is my purchase secure over the Internet?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#return">Can I return the dress if I don't like it?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#return_multiples">What if I order more than one gown, and I return the others?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#swatches">Do you send out Color Swatches?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#returnZipper">Can I return a dress that I ordered as a zipper back?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#size">What size wedding gown should I order?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#tryon">Where can I try on your dresses?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#where">Do you offer alterations?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#creditcard">I don't have a PayPal account, can I use my credit card online?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#shoppingcart">I am having trouble using the shopping cart, what do I do?</a> </li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#how">Do you ship Internationally?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#why">Do you send catalogs?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#what">Where are you located?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#when">Do you have layaway?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#Payments">What type of payments do you accept?</a></li><li><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#Shipped">How is the dress shipped?</a></li></ul><hr /><h3><br />What is the difference between buying from Bridal Online versus buying from a store or on eBay?<a name="ebay">&nbsp;</a></h3><div id="inline"><ul><li>First and foremost, <strong>selection</strong>.  The Bridal Online Store has over 195 different dress styles to choose from.  All of our gown photos were taken by a local photographer in our distribution center. The gown you see in the photos is the gown you will receive. Other sites use magazine photos or photos that are not their own.</li><li>Then, there’s <strong>availability</strong>.  We stock over 4,000 dresses in our warehouse in Dayton, Ohio, and most dresses can be shipped out the next day. </li><li>Then, of course, there’s <strong>convenience</strong>.  You can shop in the comfort of your own home or office.  You don’t even have to dress up (unless, of course, you’re at the office).  You can shop for your dress in a robe and slippers with your hair in rollers, if you want, while drinking your favorite beverage.  And let’s not forget your friends and family.  People who you might want to look at your dress, or help you decide between two or three dresses.  They can look at your choice(s) from their home or office, at their convenience.</li><li>Not only will your shopping experience with us be convenient, it will be <strong>worry free</strong>.  We have bridal sales consultants available 24 hours a day to help you find the perfect dress for the perfect price.  You can talk with them by phone (1-866-MY-GOWNS) or through our unique online chat system.  Either way, your questions will be answered in a friendly, knowledgeable manner.</li><li>Next, we offer <strong>peace of mind</strong>.  We have been in the bridal business for over 25 years, and have thousands of <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/testimonials.asp">Testimonials</a> from happy, satisfied brides.  The gown you see in the photos is the gown you will receive.  Also, unlike traditional bridal shops and other online bridal companies, we welcome exchanges and returns so you can purchase your dream dress hassle-free. Every purchase is backed by a <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">Money Back Guarantee</a>.</li><li>Finally, there’s <strong>price</strong>.  At Bridal Online you get brand new, first quality dresses at up to 80% off bridal shop prices.  We manufacturer our own dresses, and wholesale them to high end bridal shops.  We have the same dresses that are in local bridal shops.  The reason that our prices are so low is because we do not have the overhead of a bridal shop.  We are online only, that is the reason we have great prices. </li></ul><p>With over 1,000 <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/testimonials.asp">Testimonials</a> from happy, satisfied brides, we are sure to make your dream wedding possible at an affordable price.</p><p>A word about eBay. eBay is, perhaps, the largest marketplace in the world. And terrific savings can be had for many items. However, wedding dresses are not one of them. This has nothing to do with eBay, itself, but rather some unscrupulous sellers. If you're seriously thinking about purchasing your wedding dress on eBay, we urge you to read the following <strong><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/ebay.asp">case study</a></strong> before you make a bid.</p><p>If you have any further questions, we have bridal sales consultants available 24 hours a day to help. Call us at 1-866-MY-GOWNS</p><p>Please read our customers and our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/ebay.asp">eBay experiences here</a> before you search any further through eBay for your wedding gown.</p><p>If you have any further questions, we have bridal sales consultants available 24 hours a day to help. Call us at 1-866-MY-GOWNS</p></div><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br /></h3><h3>Is my purchase secure over the Internet?<a name="Secure"></a></h3><p>Your purchase could not be more secure with us.  All your sensitive information is transmitted with 128 bit encryption directly through PayPal and Google to your credit card company.  No one ever sees your credit card information. Our employees receive your name, items on your order and shipping address ONLY.  You have a better chance of having some one else having your credit card number going to a store than typing it directly on your computer.  You are also guaranteed your purchase through your credit card, PayPal and Google.</p><p>Please see our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/PrivacyPolicy.asp">Privacy Policy</a> for more details.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />Can I return the dress if I don't like it?<a name="return"></a></h3><p>Yes, our return policy is under the <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">Policy</a> button above.  All you need to do is call us for an authorization code and return the dress within three calendar days counting the day you receive your dress to get your money back (less a 10% re-stocking and shipping fee).  This is a minor risk for a great savings.  That means you need to ship it in three days, not for us to receive it in three days.  As long as the dress is in a new condition, not a custom dress and not expedited (shipped faster than regular or ground), we will happily refund your payment.</p><p>You can also <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">exchange</a> your purchase for another dress, size or color with no re-stocking fee.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />What if I order more than one gown, and I return the others?<a name="return_multiples"></a></h3><p>If you order more than one gown, as long as you keep one gown you will be given a full refund on one gown, and be charged a 10% (minimum $29) restocking fee on the other gowns that are returned. For example, if you order three gowns and return 2 gowns, you will get a full refund on one gown and be charged a restocking fee on the other. Please see our return policy <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">Here</a>.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />Do you send out Color Swatches?<a name="swatches"></a></h3><p>Yes, we can send you color swatches. Please email us at <a href="mailto:info@bridalonlinestore.com">info@bridalonlinestore.com</a> with your name and address and what colors you are wanting to see, and we will send them right out.</p><p>Please understand that these swatches are to be used only as a guide for the colors offered. Colors may vary due to dye lots and different types of fabric. Please use these swatches as a general example, as the actual gown's color may vary from that of the swatch.</p><p>We cannot guarantee gown colors to match exactly to the swatches. Dye lot variations do exist. Please use these swatches only as a reference, as they may not represent the final color of the gown.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />Can I return a dress that I custom ordered as a zipper back?<a name="returnZipper"></a></h3><p>If the gown normally comes in a lace-up back and we have made it a zipper back, it would be considered a custom and not returnable or exchangeable. Please see our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">policy</a> for more details.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />I am confused, what size wedding gown should I order?<a name="size"></a></h3><p>Wedding gowns run smaller than normal clothing sizes.  If you wear a 12 in normal clothing, you would most likely wear a 14 in a bridal gown.  The size chart is a guide, unless you are getting Corinne or Jasmine gowns, disregard the hip measurement.  If you tried on dresses in a bridal shop, order the size that fit you best.  If you wear W (Women) example: 20W, you need to add one size, so a 20W would be actually a size 22.</p><p>Please see our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/Size-Chart.asp">Size Chart</a> for more details.</p><p>Remember all wedding gowns will need minor alterations, weather you get them from us or your local bridal shop.  If you have a problem finding a seamstress in your area to do alterations at a reasonable price, we can assist you in that also.</p><p>Please see our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/alterations.asp">Alterations Page</a> for more details.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />Where can I try on your dresses?<a name="tryon"></a></h3><p>The reason that our prices are so low is because we do not have the overhead of a bridal shop.  We are mainly online, that is the reason we have great prices.  These are the same dresses that you would find in local bridal shops.  Please remember to check our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">return policy</a>, you can get your money back or exchange your dress if you are not completely satisfied.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />Do you offer alterations?<a name="where0"></a></h3><p>We have the best seamstresses in the area.  Normally, we can turn around our alteration within 7-14 days.  We recommend, however, that you find someone locally as it is much more convenient for both you and the seamstress.</p><p>We realize that many areas lack skilled bridal seamstresses, or they are very expensive.  This is the reason we offer this service. We do recommend that you approve the dress before any alterations, as the dress will not be returnable once the alterations have been completed.</p><p>Please see our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/Alterations.asp">Alterations Page</a> for more information.</p><p><br /><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3><br />I don't have a PayPal account, can I use my credit card online?<a name="creditcard"></a></h3><p>Yes, you are only using the service PayPal provides to process your credit card, you do not have to sign up with PayPal.  We actually do not recommend signing up for PayPal if you haven't already done so.  You are still covered with their insurance, and it will take 3-5 days to verify your information.  You might want to consider creating a PayPal account in the future if you do a lot of internet shopping.  </p><p>After you add all your items to your shopping cart, click on secure checkout.  You will be forwarded to the PayPal screen with payment to IBC (This is our parent company, International Bridal Company).  Depending on your browser, you will see on your screen something similar to:</p><div style="COLOR: #000000" id="xptContentOuter"><table id="table588" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center"><tbody><tr valign="top"><td><div style="COLOR: #000000" id="xptContentMain"><form method="post" action="https://www.paypal.com/us/cgi-bin/webscr"><table id="table589" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center"><tbody><tr><td class="topSpacer" width="150"><img onmouseover="function onmouseover()
