trol over the amount you are charged for customs and duties. You will have to contact your country's postal courier to determine estimated costs.</p><font color="#525139"><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p></font><hr /><h3><br />Do you send Catalogs?<a name="why"></a></h3><p>We do not have catalogues.  Our prices are so competitive that it would increase our prices significantly if we printed catalogues.  We found out most of brides are interested in one or two styles.  Most of our styles are available in your local bridal shops for two to three times the price.  With our liberal <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">return policy</a> there is nothing to fear.  </p><p>We do allow you to keep the dress for three days (counting the day you receive it) without any sales pressure a 10% re-stocking fee will be applied for refunds.  This is a minor risk for great savings!</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a><br /></p><hr /><h3><br />Where are you located?<a name="what"></a></h3><p>We are in the U.S.A., in Dayton, Ohio.  We are not a store, we are a warehouse.  The reason that our prices are so low is because we do not have the overhead of a bridal shop.  We are online only, that is the reason we have great prices.  These are the same dresses that are in local bridal shops.  Please remember to check our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/policy.asp">return policy</a>, you can get your money back or exchange.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a><br /></p><hr /><h3><br />Do You have layaway?<a name="when"></a></h3><p>Yes, we do offer layaway. To start a layaway you must pay a non-refundable $75 deposit. The layaway must be paid off within 60 days. You can pay your layaway online through our <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/collection/Payments.asp">payments button</a>, by <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/collection/ContactUs.asp">phone</a>, or by mail. If paying by <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/BridalOnlineStoreonline_orderform.pdf">mail</a> please download the <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/BridalOnlineStoreonline_orderform.pdf">Mail-In Order Form</a> and send payments to the address below with information in the letter indicating how you are paying (Weekly, Monthly, Bi-Weekly)</p><p><table style="BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse" id="table594" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" width="43%" align="center"><tbody><tr><td><div align="center">Bridal Online Payment Center<br />P O Box 750472<br />Dayton, Ohio 45475-0472<br />U.S.A.</div></td></tr></tbody></table></p><p>Out-of stock dresses are ordered from our factory when the first payment is received. Out-of-stock items can take 8-10 weeks to get in from the time the deposit is made. If you do not pay the balance within 60 days or contact us before the 60 days are up, you will lose your dress and it will need to be reordered.<br />If you are ordering a custom dress through the layaway plan, the dress will not be ordered until the full balance is paid off.</p><p>Each payment must reference the name on the initial payment.</p><p>Cancellations of layaways must email <a href="mailto:returns@bridalonlinestore.com">returns@bridalonlinestore.com</a> to cancel their order and they will be refunded what they have paid minus the $75 deposit.</p><p>If you have any questions of what your order total would be or the balance of your order is, please call us at 1-866-694-6967 or 937-291-1610.</p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a><br /></p><hr /><h3><br />What type of payments do you accept?<a name="payments"></a></h3><p>We currently accept all major credit cards or PayPal over the internet. You do not have to have a PayPal account to pay over the internet. We also accept Money Orders, Money Gram, Western Union and Wire Transfers. We can take personal checks, but all personal checks will be held 8-10 weeks for processing. No rush orders can be processed with a personal check.</p><p>To mail in and order, please download the <a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/BridalOnlineStoreonline_orderform.pdf">Mail-In Order Form</a> and send your payment to:</p><p><table style="BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse" id="table595" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" width="43%" align="center"><tbody><tr><td><div align="center">Bridal Online Payment Center<br />P O Box 750472<br />Dayton, Ohio 45475-0472<br />U.S.A.</div></td></tr></tbody></table></p><p><br />Please include the following information:</p><ul><li>Phone Number:</li><li>Style Number:</li><li>Color:</li><li>Size or measurements:</li><li>Wedding Date:</li><li>Bride's Name with City and State:</li></ul><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a></p><hr /><h3> </h3><h3>How is the dress shipped?<a name="Shipped"></a></h3><p>We will be sending you the dress the same way we send it to a bridal shop, inside-out (to protect the beading), in a box wrapped in a plastic bag to protect it from water and dirt.  After your alterations are complete and before the wedding, you will need to send your dress to be professionally steamed or pressed.  Do not try to compare the dress to the ones already pressed; it is like trying to compare wrinkled clothes to the professionally dry cleaned ones. </p><p><a href="http://wedding-dresses-sydney.com.au/admin/#top">Back to Top</a><br /></p>